title: Osteria di Fuori Porta
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Italian, Organic, Western, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Organic meals using local and seasonable products, fair trade ingredients.
